Atau kubunuh kau!

36
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:21,040
Dong-hoon?

37
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,520
Kita makan bersama.

38
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,800
Oke!

39
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:28,240
Senyum semuanya!

40
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:35,200
Liburan musim panas
sebentar lagi tiba.

41
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:37,200
Apa yang akan kita berikan
kepada guru?

42
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,800
Bagaimana kalau baju?

43
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,680
Ide bagus.
Hebat.

44
00:03:41,940 --> 00:03:44,140
Bagaimana menurutmu, Mi-hee?

45
00:03:44,780 --> 00:03:45,700
Apa?

46
00:03:47,022 --> 00:03:50,202
Kalau pot bunga bagaimana?

47
00:03:50,490 --> 00:03:51,530
Lupakan itu!

48
00:03:52,010 --> 00:03:54,050
Zaman sekarang, kita memberikan uang.

49
00:03:54,250 --> 00:03:55,570
Benar!

50
00:03:56,130 --> 00:03:58,450
Kita harus memberi berapa?

51
00:03:58,690 --> 00:04:01,610
Kau yang memutuskan, Wakil Ketua.

52
00:04:01,730 --> 00:04:03,370
Tentu.
Ya.

53
00:04:03,490 --> 00:04:04,370
Ayo.

54
00:04:04,450 --> 00:04:06,970
Nanti kukirim pesan singkat
soal berapa jumlah patungannya.

55
00:04:07,170 --> 00:04:09,210
Itu bagus.
Ya.

56
00:04:10,838 --> 00:04:13,398
Aku sudah kenyang.
Apakah hari ini kita patungan?

57
00:04:13,518 --> 00:04:14,478
Kami harus bayar berapa?

58
00:04:14,598 --> 00:04:16,478
Kita makan banyak sekali.
Ya.

59
00:04:16,878 --> 00:04:19,518
Ibu So-Won, kau akan membayarnya?

60
00:04:20,278 --> 00:04:22,078
Aku?
Kenapa tidak?

61
00:04:22,558 --> 00:04:26,118
Bagaimana kalau kali ini
kita berdua yang membayarnya?

62
00:04:26,598 --> 00:04:27,958
Aku bahkan tak ikut makan.

63
00:04:28,078 --> 00:04:32,598
Dia terlalu sibuk di toko
dan jarang keluar rumah.

64
00:04:33,158 --> 00:04:36,238
Dia selalu bilang
bahwa dia harus mentraktir kalian.

65
00:04:36,398 --> 00:04:39,838
Bagaimana jika kita beri kesempatan
pada Ibu So-Won?

66
00:04:40,078 --> 00:04:41,478
Kenapa tidak?

67
00:04:41,638 --> 00:04:45,638
Terima kasih, Ny. Im.
Terima kasih.

68
00:04:47,348 --> 00:04:48,788
Kau punya uang berapa?

69
00:04:52,068 --> 00:04:53,628
Aku punya $20.

70
00:04:54,228 --> 00:04:55,468
Bisa pakai kartu kredit?

71
00:05:00,062 --> 00:05:02,782
Totalnya $198? Itu gila.

72
00:05:03,422 --> 00:05:05,862
Dasar para wanita pemakan daging.

73
00:05:06,262 --> 00:05:08,062
Itu untuk menarik simpati mereka.

74
00:05:08,222 --> 00:05:11,262
Atau anakmu akan dikucilkan.

75
00:05:11,852 --> 00:05:12,732
"Semangka $ 20"

76
00:05:12,852 --> 00:05:14,772
Kenapa mahal sekali?

77
00:05:16,972 --> 00:05:20,452
Suruh suami
menaikkan gaji ayahnya So-Won.

78
00:05:20,932 --> 00:05:23,892
Dia cuma manajer, bukan bos.

79
00:05:26,086 --> 00:05:28,966
Omong-omong, kau akan memberitahunya?

80
00:05:29,606 --> 00:05:32,606
Bagaimana dia bisa tidak tahu?
Sepertinya bayimu laki-laki.

81
00:05:32,806 --> 00:05:34,966
Dia tidak peduli padaku.

82
00:05:35,286 --> 00:05:38,766
Lalu bagaimana
kau bisa hamil?

83
00:05:40,818 --> 00:05:44,738
Kami melakukannya sekali dalam 3 tahun
dan aku langsung hamil.

84
00:05:45,618 --> 00:05:47,218
3 tahun?

85
00:05:47,778 --> 00:05:50,618
Suamiku selalu menggerayangiku.

86
00:05:50,778 --> 00:05:53,138
Dia selalu merasa tidak puas.

87
00:05:53,298 --> 00:05:56,218
Bagaimana caraku membesarkan 2 anak
jika satu saja sudah sulit?

88
00:05:56,338 --> 00:05:57,618
Dasar.

89
00:05:58,018 --> 00:06:01,738
Lahirkan bayinya.
Dia akan besar sendiri.

90
00:06:05,016 --> 00:06:06,576
Benar-benar tak ada lagi?

91
00:06:07,376 --> 00:06:08,416
Ya.

92
00:06:09,656 --> 00:06:11,896
Tidak setia kawan!

93
00:06:21,828 --> 00:06:24,068
Im Dong-hoon, rasanya enak?

94
00:06:24,868 --> 00:06:26,148
Ya.

95
00:06:28,628 --> 00:06:30,468
Aku cuma makan satu.
Sumpah.

96
00:06:30,668 --> 00:06:32,628
Tulang-tulang itu
mustahil dari satu potong ayam.

97
00:06:36,258 --> 00:06:37,138
Suka?

98
00:06:37,378 --> 00:06:38,418
Ini enak.

99
00:06:39,778 --> 00:06:41,378
Memangnya di rumah kau tak makan?

100
00:06:41,498 --> 00:06:43,458
Makan, tapi cuma nasi.

101
00:06:44,578 --> 00:06:48,418
Aku kurus, tapi istriku semakin gemuk.

102
00:06:49,018 --> 00:06:50,178
Bagus kalau begitu.

103
00:06:51,212 --> 00:06:53,492
Di rumah dan di sini aku tak makan.

104
00:06:54,132 --> 00:06:56,412
Di rumah dan di sini cuma makan nasi.

105
00:06:56,652 --> 00:07:00,492
Ketiga anakku bilang aku bau
dan mereka tak mau mendekatiku.

106
00:07:04,104 --> 00:07:05,344
Mau?

107
00:07:06,744 --> 00:07:08,424
Lupakan saja.
Baiklah.

108
00:07:18,938 --> 00:07:21,778
Berikan padaku.
Kau punya tiga kartu sama.

109
00:07:21,938 --> 00:07:24,218
Tapi kartu ini langka.

110
00:07:24,778 --> 00:07:26,298
Kartumu tidak.

111
00:07:26,658 --> 00:07:27,738
Mau?

112
00:07:28,578 --> 00:07:30,458
Ayo tukar dengan ini.

113
00:07:31,386 --> 00:07:33,626
Satu kartu ini untuk lima kartu itu.

114
00:07:34,106 --> 00:07:36,866
Young-Suk, kau curang.

115
00:07:37,066 --> 00:07:39,426
Tidak mau! Curang!
Ayo.

116
00:07:59,464 --> 00:08:00,624
Apa?

117
00:08:01,864 --> 00:08:02,704
Apa?

118
00:08:14,702 --> 00:08:16,302
Tunggu.

119
00:08:32,382 --> 00:08:34,702
Aku mati lagi.
Menyebalkan.

120
00:08:35,736 --> 00:08:36,496
Hei!

121
00:08:36,616 --> 00:08:37,896
Han Young-seok!

122
00:08:38,216 --> 00:08:38,896
Apa?

123
00:08:39,016 --> 00:08:41,456
Itu bukan milikmu.
Jangan dipukul.

124
00:08:42,442 --> 00:08:46,202
Aku membayar untuk memainkan ini.
Jangan ikut campur.

125
00:08:47,162 --> 00:08:50,242
Dasar bocah cilik.

126
00:08:51,282 --> 00:08:52,402
Cilik?

127
00:08:59,974 --> 00:09:02,534
Baiklah. Wajahmu jauh lebih besar.
Jadi begitu?

128
00:09:02,774 --> 00:09:04,134
Awas kau!

129
00:09:05,054 --> 00:09:06,974
Ibu, aku pulang!

130
00:09:07,734 --> 00:09:08,934
Hai, So-Won.

131
00:09:18,690 --> 00:09:21,290
Young-seok biang masalah.

132
00:09:21,570 --> 00:09:23,210
Kenapa menggerutu?

133
00:09:28,250 --> 00:09:29,330
Cicipi ini.

134
00:09:33,610 --> 00:09:36,530
Aku tak mengerti sama sekali.

135
00:09:36,850 --> 00:09:37,810
Mengerti apa?

136
00:09:38,010 --> 00:09:40,730
Soal matematika ini.

137
00:09:41,170 --> 00:09:44,130
Aku bisa menjawab hampir semua soal.

138
00:09:44,970 --> 00:09:47,570
Tapi yang satu soal ini
sama sekali tak bisa.

139
00:09:47,890 --> 00:09:50,730
Kenapa soal matematika Kelas 2 SD
sangat sulit?

140
00:09:50,890 --> 00:09:52,250
Baca sekali lagi.

141
00:09:52,938 --> 00:09:54,498
Haruskah aku tanya Ayah?

142
00:09:54,658 --> 00:09:55,658
Ayah?

143
00:09:55,938 --> 00:09:58,538
Kemungkinan dia tidak lebih tahu
daripada ibu.

144
00:10:00,182 --> 00:10:01,262
Ayo makan!

145
00:10:01,462 --> 00:10:07,062
Young-su punya 9 pensil
dan Jin-hee punya 3.

146
00:10:07,502 --> 00:10:11,622
Bagaimana agar jumlah pensil mereka
menjadi sama?

147
00:10:11,782 --> 00:10:14,022
Tulis jawabanmu.

148
00:10:15,780 --> 00:10:17,780
Lalu?
Apa jawabanmu?

149
00:10:17,980 --> 00:10:19,100
Belum kujawab.

150
00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:20,820
Kenapa?

151
00:10:21,540 --> 00:10:26,900
Tambahkan saja angka 9 dan 3,
lalu dibagi dua.

152
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:30,420
Tidak semudah itu.

153
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:34,620
Anggap saja Young-su adalah
Young-seok.

154
00:10:35,100 --> 00:10:37,460
Dan Jin-hee adalah aku.

155
00:10:38,778 --> 00:10:39,778
Young-seok?

156
00:10:40,218 --> 00:10:44,898
Tidak mungkin
Young-seok akan memberikan pensilnya.

157
00:10:46,298 --> 00:10:51,138
Agar jumlah pensil kami sama,
dia harus memberiku tiga pensilnya.

158
00:10:52,298 --> 00:10:56,538
Tidak mungkin
dia akan memberiku sesuatu.

159
00:10:56,938 --> 00:10:59,618
Bukan itu jawabannya.

160
00:11:01,958 --> 00:11:04,678
Dong-hoon, katakan sesuatu.

161
00:11:06,238 --> 00:11:08,078
Dengarkan apa kata ibumu.

162
00:11:08,238 --> 00:11:10,358
Jangan memulai pertengkaran dengannya.

163
00:11:18,018 --> 00:11:20,578
Mi pedas membuat maagku kambuh.

164
00:11:20,698 --> 00:11:23,218
Kalau begitu jangan dimakan!
Aku tidak bilang tidak mau mi ini.

165
00:11:23,378 --> 00:11:25,698
Lupakan saja.
Nonton bisbol sana!

166
00:11:26,018 --> 00:11:27,858
Aku akan membesarkan
So-Won sendirian.

167
00:11:28,738 --> 00:11:29,978
Sungguh?

168
00:11:32,418 --> 00:11:34,458
Dengarkan ibumu baik-baik.

169
00:11:37,858 --> 00:11:39,058
Bodoh!

170
00:11:46,270 --> 00:11:49,070
Ayo tidur di kasur.

171
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:54,150
Kokomong si sosis

172
00:11:54,670 --> 00:11:57,470
Kokomong yang suka bercanda

173
00:11:57,950 --> 00:12:00,910
Kokomong penemu yang hebat

174
00:12:01,430 --> 00:12:04,470
Kokomong pemimpin anak-anak

175
00:12:06,242 --> 00:12:08,442
Young-seok, kau menunggu So-Won?

176
00:12:08,922 --> 00:12:12,682
Tidak mungkin.
Aku tidak menunggu So-Won.

177
00:12:13,082 --> 00:12:14,562
Lalu kau sedang apa di sini?

178
00:12:14,802 --> 00:12:16,722
Aku menunggu teman-temanku.

179
00:12:17,770 --> 00:12:18,970
Ayo!
Oke! Ayo!

180
00:12:19,090 --> 00:12:21,650
Tapi So-Won sebentar lagi keluar.

181
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:26,360
Ayah, bisa mengikat rambutku?

182
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:28,440
Tentu bisa.

183
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,680
Kemarilah.

184
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:33,960
Duduk.

185
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:38,200
Gwang-Sik

186
00:12:45,980 --> 00:12:47,900
Aku mau berangkat.

187
00:12:49,380 --> 00:12:51,260
Anak keduamu sakit?

188
00:12:52,700 --> 00:12:55,020
Flu? Ya ampun.

189
00:12:55,700 --> 00:12:57,860
Aku bisa sampai sana 20 menit lagi.

190
00:13:01,176 --> 00:13:06,256
Tanda tangani barang yang masuk,
lalu buka pabriknya?

191
00:13:06,416 --> 00:13:08,096
Oke. Dah.

192
00:13:10,056 --> 00:13:11,776
Tak usah.

193
00:13:11,804 --> 00:13:12,964
Kenapa?

194
00:13:14,164 --> 00:13:15,444
Ayah akan mengikatnya
dengan cantik.

195
00:13:15,604 --> 00:13:16,644
Lupakan saja!

196
00:13:17,044 --> 00:13:20,044
Aku selalu hanya menjepit rambutku.

197
00:13:21,684 --> 00:13:23,884
Ibu selalu sibuk!

198
00:13:24,004 --> 00:13:27,444
Kau lebih cantik
jika rambutmu dijepit.

199
00:13:37,260 --> 00:13:38,580
So-Won sudah ke sekolah, kan?

200
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:39,780
Dia masih di rumah.

201
00:13:39,900 --> 00:13:41,860
Ya ampun, dia terlambat!
Baik.

202
00:13:42,100 --> 00:13:43,900
Anak-anak lain sudah berangkat!

203
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:46,340
Aku harus pergi mengecek barang masuk.

204
00:13:46,940 --> 00:13:48,060
Mana payungnya?

205
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:50,500
Cari di bawah mesin kas.

206
00:13:50,660 --> 00:13:51,180
Oke.

207
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:54,380
So-Won, kau bisa terlambat!

208
00:14:15,306 --> 00:14:16,826
Apa yang..

209
00:14:36,948 --> 00:14:38,388
"Kami Segera Kembali"

210
00:14:42,628 --> 00:14:44,508
Aku basah! Lari!

211
00:14:45,028 --> 00:14:47,068
Hei, lewat sini!

212
00:14:52,178 --> 00:14:53,578
So-Won!

213
00:14:54,898 --> 00:14:55,698
Ya?

214
00:14:56,578 --> 00:14:57,978
Jangan merengut.

215
00:14:59,324 --> 00:15:02,364
Besok ibu ikat rambutmu
hingga cantik.

216
00:15:02,484 --> 00:15:03,964
Ibu selalu bilang begitu!

217
00:15:04,684 --> 00:15:06,244
Sudah besar, ya?

218
00:15:06,644 --> 00:15:08,604
Berani membantah ibu?

219
00:15:11,816 --> 00:15:15,096
Mau ibu antar ke sekolah?

220
00:15:15,296 --> 00:15:18,376
Tidak usah.
Aku bisa lari ke sana dalam 3 menit.

221
00:15:19,136 --> 00:15:24,296
Jangan lewat gang-gang becek
dan lewat jalan besar saja.

222
00:15:25,224 --> 00:15:26,864
Aku memang ingin lewat jalan besar.

223
00:15:30,744 --> 00:15:32,664
Lewat jalan besar!

224
00:15:32,864 --> 00:15:37,024
"VIENNA PIANO"

225
00:16:18,102 --> 00:16:21,142
Jika terlambat, celaka kita!
Lari!

226
00:16:22,142 --> 00:16:24,582
Hujannya deras sekali!
Aku kedinginan!

227
00:16:26,182 --> 00:16:29,702
Tunggu aku!
Jangan cepat-cepat!

228
00:16:41,662 --> 00:16:43,782
Cepat!

229
00:16:52,062 --> 00:16:53,982
Tunggu!

230
00:17:12,232 --> 00:17:13,712
Mau ke sekolah?

231
00:17:16,872 --> 00:17:19,112
Payungmu cantik sekali.

232
00:17:25,072 --> 00:17:27,152
Boleh aku ikut dipayungi?

233
00:17:29,466 --> 00:17:30,666
Tapi..

234
00:17:30,866 --> 00:17:32,986
Aku terlambat ke sekolah.

235
00:17:51,300 --> 00:17:54,500
Mereka masuk sekarang.
Akan kuhitung semuanya.

236
00:17:55,020 --> 00:17:55,980
Jangan cemas.

237
00:17:56,180 --> 00:17:57,260
Hati-hati.

238
00:18:05,396 --> 00:18:07,996
Kenapa tagihan gas tinggi sekali?

239
00:18:54,978 --> 00:18:55,818
Ya?

240
00:18:56,018 --> 00:18:57,138
Kau di mana?

241
00:18:57,938 --> 00:18:59,258
Di rumah.

242
00:18:59,578 --> 00:19:01,138
Ya Tuhan.

243
00:19:01,418 --> 00:19:03,458
Apa? Ada masalah?

244
00:19:04,658 --> 00:19:08,058
Ada banyak polisi
di luar sekolah.

245
00:19:10,168 --> 00:19:11,128
Sekolah?

246
00:19:11,648 --> 00:19:15,368
